Mitsuru Kono is the principal architect of Erwiz which formerly was Erviz. Since
the Erviz project seems to be discontinued it was forked and rebranded as Erwiz.
The Erwiz distribution is maintained by Romain Schmitz.

We acknowledge the substantial contributions to the Erwiz project by
these gifted individuals (listed in alphabetical order):

Mitsuru Kono
	Authored the Erviz code base and worked on the English and Japanese translations.
	
Romain Schmitz
	Maintains the current Erwiz project and Linux packages.
